data.description: This custom home was designed to feel like a private estate. All while being a short distance to schools, shopping and dining. The private gated entrance, driveway and fencing make for a great first impression. The home has been thoughtfully designed to offer formal and informal living spaces. With attention to details and custom touches throughout. The main level Primary Suite is luxurious in details and design, Featuring private deck access. A well-appointed bath with custom shower, jetted soaker tub, designer hardware and heated floor. The kitchen is a chef's delight. With ample cabinets and counter space, appliances and functionality. Opening into an informal dining area and keeping room with fireplace. The second floor contains.   2 family bedrooms, bath and large bonus room with closet.  Rear main level deck and lower-level patios perfect for indoor / outdoor living spaces. The whole lower level is framed and plumbed for future expansion. It can house a second kitchen, family room, a 4th bedroom and a 3rd full bath. As well as an exercise space and home theater. There's even space for a second laundry or wine cellar. While still offering plenty of storage. Quality poured concrete construction in the walk out basement. The lot has been prepped for a pool for further future relaxation. Seller also has plans for an additional 3 car detached garage with studio above. Offering a multitude of further expansion. All appliances and living room surround sound and TV will convey. Propane tank is not leased and will convey.
